values: Well, first I'm HOME. Yay! The other entries were of me at my parents(with out songs on them). Anyways, my Grandpa's home, and he's doing great. ^^ He'll have the surgery in 2 weeks. They moved it up. He acts normal, you would never know he had cancer. He's still goofy as ever. Lol..well, I'm gonna go finish watching <u>Enough</u>. Then <u>Reign of Fire</u>. Muwahaha. Bye!

Yeah, this is public. Well, I think I might shut down my journals. No reason to keep them. I have a journal in real life(Actually, it's a notebook I never used for school, but yeah)and I wrote my stuff and feelings down into it. I just don't know if I should have an online journal. I don't like people reading my stuff. So, yeah. 

Anyways, I'm sorry, Andrew. I wish you the best of luck in school. (If I haven't unblocked you and stuff by then).

Okay, whoever you are you immature bastard, you can see this entry because it's PUBLIC. And I mean this to whoever the hell is posting shit in Jessie's LJ. Just know that we have your IP, can and WILL report you to the people at livejournal, AND will tell Kaitou. Here's some free advice from me: GET A DAMN LIFE AND GROW THE HELL UP.

Okay, I am SICK of being lied to by my parents, I can't depend on them, I KNEW I couldn't depend on them.



Oh, and if any of YOU reading this wanna bash my ass by saying how I want attention, how I need to relax, how I need to be positive right now FUCK THE HELL OFF. -_-; Call me a bitch, I don't care!

For all you dumbasses who don't know what the picture means, it means I love Jean. ...And that this journal is friends only. If you're a friend of mine that just got a LiveJournal, either IM me or post a comment here. Or, if you're someone looking for a friend, I'll be more than happy to talk to you. But you have to be open-minded, not a stuck-up bitch/bastard, or the most evil bitch in town. Feel free to contact me.
E-mail: gothicjester@hotmail.com AIM: zhazeleyedz Tuxedo BBS: Aeris Gainsborough
